title: The Ghost
body:
The imdb listing of full cast and crew for S2 E2 Nice and Neat shows a character called Jin. I’m pretty sure we only ever saw the back of her head, the “invisible woman,” as the cleaner.

An interesting bit of wordplay in her (choice of?) name, not a ghost but perhaps a spirit?

On a lighter note: in direct contrast to Villanelle’s description of The Ghost as a “big, fat nobody”…

I’m sure that very important quarter inch will make all the difference when Villanelle (Jodie) is a shade over 5’ 8" 🤣

Tl,dr The Ghost is probably a smol asian lady called Jin and I cannot WAIT for Villanelle to tower over her in disbelief.

(Also go check out her show reel on imdb, attitude for days)
